						Public Code US has not reviewed all of the sites linked to its website and is not responsible for the contents of any such linked site. The inclusion of any link does not imply endorsement by Public Code US of the site. Use of any such linked website is at the user's own risk.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border-4 border-am-dark bg-am-light p-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">8. Modifications</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark">
						Public Code US may revise these terms of service at any time without notice. By using this website, you are agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these terms of service.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div>
